description:
This is a 34 minute workout called 'First Trimester Pregnancy Exercises | 30 Minute Pregnancy Workout First Trimester' from the channel Pregnancy and Postpartum TV.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Today we are doing first trimester pregnancy exercises! These are designed to give you more energy and relieve any nausea from morning sickness. I hope you feel great after this 30-minute pregnancy workout for first trimester. I have provided safe modifications for second and third trimester as well.
